\id GAL - Drafted 1995; revised during workshop with Mike Sweeney; checked with John/Marsha Relyea and 3 Aruamu groups; consultant check with Mike Sweeney. Revised by Aruamu translation team in 2019-2020, with input from many Aruamus.
\h Galesia
\toc3 GAL
\toc2 Galesia
\toc1 Ak…®nafarir Pol Galesian Provins…®n Itir Sios Bagha Osirizim
\mt1 Ak…®nafarir Pol Galesian Provins…®n Itir Sios Bagha Osirizim
\mt2 O
\mt1 Galesia
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim
\ip Gumazamizir faragha Iesus…®n g…®n zuiba, me Judan gumazamizibara. Ez…® g…®n Iesus Pol amadaz…®ma, a ghua Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba uaghan Akar Aghuim me m…®k…®ri. Ez…® gumazamizir kaba Iesus…®n g…®n zuima, os…®mt…®zir mam oto. Fom…®ra gumazamizir kaba Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®, mati Judaba ami mok…®n. Egha me Krais…®n g…®n zuima, azangs…®zir ekiam kamagh…®n iti: me uaghan Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n mangam, o puvat…®gham?
\ip Gumazir maba kamagh…®n ifonge, me gumazir kabar amut…® me Judabar arazim…®n g…®n mang…® uan m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghoregh Moses Osirizir Arazir igharazibar g…®n mangam. Ez…® Pol ghaze, puvat…®. A ghaze, e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais Iesus…®n iti, ez…® bizir kamra e gamima, e God…®n damazim…®n gumazamizir aghuibar otivigha ik…®r…®m…®rir igiam ini.
\ip Judan gumazir kabar maba ti faragha Galesian Provins…®n ghuegha Krais…®n adarazigh amima, me Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n mangasava ami. Pol bizir otozir kam baregha, ua Galesiabar n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba ko arazibar k…®rasa, ak…®nafarir kam me bagha an osiri.
\ip Pol ak…®nafarir kam…®n faragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, God uab…® Aposel…®n ingangarim damuasava anem…®sefe. A uab…® uan ifongiam…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®gha, gumazitam…®n akam…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®. God an diagha egha Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba Akar Aghuim akunamin ingangarim a gan…®ngi. Ak…®nafarir kam…®n, Pol ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais Iesus…®n itiba, merara God…®n damazim…®n deragha iti. Ak…®nafarir kam…®n akar abuananaba kamak…®n, Krais e f…®rizima, God…®n Duam tuavim en akaz…®ma, e arazir aghuibar igharaz darazigh ami.
\c 1
\ms1 God aposel…®n ingangarim damuasa Pol am…®sefe
\mr (Sapta 1:1--2:14)
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Galesia 1:11-12\x*K…® Pol. Nguazir kam…®n gumazitam o amizitam aposel…®n ikiasa na m…®sevegha ingangarir kam na gan…®ngizir puvat…®. God, en Afeziar Iesus gamiz…® a ua d…®kavizim, a ko Ekiam Krais Iesus, aning aposel…®n ikiasa na m…®sefe.
\v 2 K…®, na ko itir darazi ko, e Galesian Provins…®n itir Krais…®n adarazi bagha ak…®nafarir kam amadi.
\p 
\v 3-5 \x - \xo 1:3-5 \xt Rom 1:7; Filipai 1:2; Rom 4:25; Galesia 2:20; 1 Timoti 2:6; Taitus 2:14; 1 Jon 5:19\x*Dat…®r…®gh…®n e nguazir kam…®n itima, arazir kuraba bar e ikiava e adafi. Ez…® God en Afeziam en akurvaghasa ifonge. Ez…® kamagh…®n Ekiam Krais Iesus en arazir kuraba batogh…®va, en akurvaghasava areme. En Afeziam God ko Ekiam Krais Iesus, aning apangkuvim ko navir am…®rizim ian ikia, egha kamagh…®n ami. Eght…® gumazamiziba zurazurara ziar ekiam God dan…®ng mamagh…®ra ikiam. Bar guizbang…®ra.
\s1 K…® gari, ia God atagh…®razima, kamagh…®n k…® d…®gavir kuram gami
\p 
\v 6 K…® faragha Krais…®n Akar Aghuim…®n ia m…®kemez…®, ia fo, Krais…®n apangkuvim ian iti. Ia foz…®, kamagh…®n God ian d…®a ghaze, ia iz…®. Ez…® ia zuam…®ra God…®n ian diazim ataki. Egha ia akar aghuir igharazim…®n g…®n zui. Ez…® kamagh…®n k…® ian arazir kam…®n d…®gavir kuram gami.
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Aposel 15:1; 15:24; 2 Korin 2:17; 11:4; 11:13\x*Ia ghaze, ia akar aghuir igharazim…®n g…®n zui. Bar puvat…®, akar aghuir igharazitam ua itir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazamizir maba Krais…®n Akar Aghuim giraghava akar ifavaribar amuasa. Egha ia gamiz…®, ia okam n…®ghn…®si.
\v 8 Eght…® e uari, o God…®n Nguibam…®n ensel…®n tam Akar Aghuir e faragha ia m…®k…®nizim ia m…®k…®nighan kogh, egh akar igharazitam ia m…®k…®nigham, egh gumazamizir kaba, hel…®n mang…® zurara ik…®.
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt God…®n Araziba 4:2; Aghuzir Akaba 30:6; Akar Mogomem 22:18-19\x*E faragha ia m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ua ia m…®gei. Gumazamizitaba akar igharazitam ia m…®k…®night…®, an Akar Aghuir ia faragha g…®n zuim…®n m…®n mangan koght…®, gumazamizir kaba hel…®n mang…®va zurara ik…®!
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt 1 Tesalonika 2:4\x*Ia manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®si? K…® ian navibar amut…® da deraghasa, k…® ti m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam gamiz? O k…® God…®n navim damut…® a deraghasa, k…® ti m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam gami? K…® gumazamizibar damazim…®n ziam iniasa, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam gami, o? Bar puvat…®. K…® ingangarir kam damu, gumazamizibar damazim…®n ziam iniva, egh kamagh…®n k…® Krais…®n ingangarir gumazim…®n ikian kogham.
\s1 Nguazim…®n gumazamizitaba akar k…® ia m…®k…®rir kam na gan…®ngizir puvat…®
\p 
\v 11-12 \x - \xo 1:11-12 \xt Matyu 16:17; 1 Korin 15:1-3; Galesia 1:1; Efesus 3:3\x*Nan adarasi, k…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei. K…® ti pura gumazitam o amizitam…®n akam ia m…®k…®niz…® ia anetegha akar igharazim…®n g…®n zuima, k…® ti d…®gavir kuram gamighan koghai. Ez…® gumazamiziba Akar Aghuir kam na gan…®ngizir puvat…®. Egha gumazamiziba akar kam nan sure gamizir puvat…®. Krais Iesus uab…® Akar Aghuir kam nan akaz…® k…® a g…®fo. Kamagh…®n ia foghasa, k…® ia m…®gei, Akar Aghuir k…® ia m…®k…®nizim, kar puram akar gumazamizitabar akam…®n otozir puvat…®zim.
\p 
\v 13-14 \x - \xo 1:13-14 \xt Aposel 8:3; 9:1; 22:3-5; 26:9-11; Filipai 3:6; 1 Timoti 1:13\x*K…® eghaghanitam ia damut…® ia fogh suam, bizir k…® m…®geir kaba da guizbang…®ra. Nan Judan ovavibar araziba ik…®v…®ra ikiasa, kamagh…®n k…® pamtem dar g…®n zui. K…® Judan Araziba bar dar g…®n ghua, kamagh…®n k…® Judan igiar na ko aghungizibagh afira. Kamagh…®n k…® Krais…®n adarazigh as…®ghas…®ghasa os…®mt…®ziba me gar…®si. K…® Judan Arazibar g…®n ghua arazir kam gamiz…®, ia a baraki. (Ia fo, dughiar kam k…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n Akar Aghuim…®n itir puvat…®gha, arazir kabagh ami.)
\v 15-17 \x - \xo 1:15-17 \xt Aisaia 49:1; Jeremaia 1:5; Aposel 9:3-6; 9:15; 22:6-10; 26:13-18; Rom 1:1; 11:13; Galesia 2:7\x*Nan amebam t…®ghar na batamin dughiam…®n God aposel…®n ikiasa na ginaba. Egha g…®n a nan apangkuvigha ingangarir kam damuasa nan dia. Egha kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® nan otarim…®n Akar Aghuim…®n gun Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibav k…®nasa, k…® ifonge. Bizir kam bagha a uan otarim nan akaghasa ifonge. Ez…® k…® magh…®ra Akar Aghuim gumazamizibav k…®nasa ua tav…®n azarazir puvat…®. Dughiar kam k…® aposel…®n faragha ingariba bagha Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghuavanabozir puvat…®. K…® magh…®ra Arebian kantrin ghugha g…®n uamategha Damaskus…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghu.
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Aposel 9:26-30\x*Egha g…®n azenir pumuning ko m…®kezim g…®vaz…®ma, k…® Pita g…®fogh…®va a ko m…®k…®masa Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghuavanabo. K…® ghugha 15plan dughiabar a ko ike.
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Matyu 13:55\x*Dughiar kam k…® Ekiam…®n dozim, Jemsra gani. Egha k…® aposel…®n igharazitam uam an ganizir puvat…®.
\v 20 Ia oregh fogh suam nguazim…®n gumazamiziba Akar Aghuir k…® ia m…®k…®nizir kam na m…®kemezir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n ia fogh suam, eghaghanir k…® eghara ak…®nafarim…®n osirir kamnagh, a guizbang…®ra. God fo.
\v 21-23 \x - \xo 1:21-23 \xt Aposel 9:30\x*Egha k…® g…®n Jerusalem ategha ghua Sirian Provins ko Silisian Provins bar aning…®n aven arui. K…® kamagh…®n amima, Judian Distrigh…®n aven itir Krais…®n adarazi me tong nan guam…®n ganizir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazamizir maba ghaze, Pol fom…®ra en n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir God…®n itim gas…®ghas…®ghasa os…®mt…®ziba e gar…®si. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n gumazir kamra God…®n Akar Aghuim gumazamizibav k…®ra ghaze, ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n ik…®.
\v 24 Judian Distrigh…®n itir gumazamiziba orazi, God nan n…®ghn…®zibagh iraz…®ma, me bizir kam bagha God…®n ziam fe.
\c 2
\s1 Aposel…®n igharaziba, Pol ko uari inigha navir vam…®ra iti
\p 
\v 1-3 \x - \xo 2:1-3 \xt Aposel 11:30; 15:2; 16:3\x*K…® kamagh…®n atiati, Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba g…®n Judan Araziba me ik…®rarigham. K…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, gumazamizir kaba Judan Arazibar g…®n mang…®t…®, ingangarir k…® fom…®ram amizim ko ingangarir dat…®r…®gh…®n amim aning pura ingangarir k…®nim gavagham. K…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zima, God bizir kam nan akagha ghaze, n…® Jerusalem…®n mangasa k…® ifonge. K…® fom…®ra Jerusalem…®n ghuavanaboz…®, 14pla azeniba dat…®r…®gh…®n g…®vaz…®, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n God nan akazir bizim…®n m…®rara k…® uamategha Jerusalem…®n ghuavanabo. K…® ghua Barnabas ko ghua, egha Taitus uaghan a inigha ghu. E ghuegha, k…® Krais…®n adarazir ziaba itir gumazir dapanibara, me akuvaghava, Akar Aghuir k…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibav kemezimra, k…® me m…®gei. Taitus, na ko ghuzir gumazim, a Grigh…®n gumazimra. K…® Akar Aghuir Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibav geir kamra gumazir dapanibav geima, me oregha Taitus…®n m…®karzir mogomem…®n inim aghorasa a gaghorir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Aposel 15:1; 15:24; 2 Korin 11:20; 11:26; Galesia 1:7; 5:1; 5:13\x*Taitus…®n m…®karzir mogomem…®n inim aghorir m…®g…®r…®g…®am…®n m…®ngarim kamagh…®n oto. Gumazir ifavarir maba mogomem…®n en tong…®n ize. Me e gifara mati me guizbang…®ra en marasi. Me orazi, e fom…®ra Judan Arazibar apengan itima, da e ikiaghar…®ki, ez…® Iesus e gamiz…®ma, e dat…®r…®gh…®n f…®riagh…®r…®. Ez…® gumazir kaba Krais e f…®rizir arazibar ganasa iza ifarava en tong…®n iti. Gumazir kaba e damut…® e ua Judan Arazibar apengan ik…®t…® da uam e ik…®rar…®ghasa, me ifonge. Egha me Taitus…®n m…®karzir mogomem…®n inim aghorasa, e m…®gei.
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Galesia 3:1\x*Ez…® e ghaze, Akar Aghuim a guizbang…®ra m…®g…®r…®g…®am, ez…® a ia ko ik…®v…®ra ikiasa, e ifonge. Kamagh…®n e me baragha tong men akabar g…®n zuir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt God…®n Araziba 10:17; Aposel 10:34; Rom 2:11; 2 Korin 12:11; Galesia 6:3\x*Ez…® Jerusalem…®n itir gumazir dapaniba, me akar otevir igharazitam nan m…®g…®r…®g…®am isafurazir puvat…®. Gumazir kaba me gumazir dapaniba, a dera. God gumazir ziaba itibar garir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, tina ziam iti, o tina ziam pu, nan n…®ghn…®zim, ziar ekiam pura bizim. K…® m…®geima gumazir dapaniba oraghava kamagh…®n m…®geir puvat…®, ‚ÄúN…® paza bizir mabav gei.‚Äù Egha me bar akar otevir igharazitam nan m…®g…®r…®g…®am isafurazir puvat…®.
\v 7-9 \x - \xo 2:7-9 \xt Aposel 22:21; Rom 1:5; Efesus 3:8\x*God faragha Judan gumazamizibar tong…®n aposel…®n ingangarim damuasa, Pita ginaba. Egha ingangarim damuasa gavgavim a gan…®ngi. Egha Akar Aghuim Judan gumazamizibav k…®nasa Pita m…®keme. Kamagh…®ra God Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibar tong…®n aposel…®n ingangarim damuasa, k…® Pol na ginaba, egha God uab…® gavgavim na gan…®ngi. Egha ghaze, n…® Pol n…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba Akar Aghuim me m…®k…®n. Krais…®n adarazir gumazir dapanir pumuning ko m…®kezim, Jems, Pita ko Jon, me nan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baregha, fo, God uab…® ingangarir kam na gan…®ngi. Me fo, God…®n apangkuvim na ko itima, a ingangarir kam na gan…®ngi. Me kamagh…®n fogha, bar akar otevir vam…®ra na ko Barnabas gan…®ngi, ‚ÄúE Judan gumazamizibar tong…®n ingart…®, n…® ko Barnabas Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibar tong…®n ingar.
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Aposel 11:29-30\x*Gua me ko ingar…®va gumazamizir onganarazir Jerusalem…®n itiba, gua men akurvaghamin n…®ghn…®zim g…®namangan mark…®.‚Äù K…® fom…®ra akurvazir kam gamua iza dat…®r…®gh…®n a damuasa ifongegha nan n…®ghn…®zim a bagha bar gavgafi. Egha e ingangarim kamagh…®n aneb…®gha uari ganigha, egh n…®ghn…®zir vam…®ra ikiasa uan agharibar suisi.
\s1 K…® gari, Pita arazir kuram gamima k…® an anogoroke
\p 
\v 11-13 \x - \xo 2:11-13 \xt Aposel 11:3\x*Dughiar mam Pita Antiogh…®n nguibar ekiam…®n izegha, Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba koma api. Ez…® g…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itir Judan marazi me Jems ko ikegha uaghan Antiogh…®n ize. Me izez…®, Pita kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, k…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba ko ik…® dam…®t…®, Judaba me m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghorezir darasi, me nan ataram. A kamagh…®n atiatigha, Judan izezir darazigh ifara, egha Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba me ategha saghon ikiasa. Egha a Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba koma uam apir puvat…®. Egha Judabar gumaziba me koma api. An arazir kam gamiz…®, Judan Antiogh…®n itir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itir darasi, me uaghan Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba ko ik…® daman aghua. Me ifavarir arazir kam gamima, Barnabas uaghan men m…®n ami. Ez…® gumazir kaba Pitan arazir ifavarim…®n g…®n zui. Ez…® an arazir kurar kam azenim gir…®z…® me bar fo, an arazir kuram gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Pitan arazir kurar kam bagha an guam gat…®gha an atari.
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt 1 Timoti 5:20\x*Me Akar Aghuim…®n guizbang…®ra m…®g…®r…®g…®aba derav…®ra dar g…®n zui puvat…®. Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n men arazir kurabar ganigha, Pita men damazim…®n kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúPita, n…® Judabar gumazir mam, egha n…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais Iesus…®n iti, egha n…® Judan Araziba ategha, Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibar arazir mabagh ami. Gumazir maba Jems ko ikegha izez…®ma, n…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibar araziba ategha, manmaghsua ua Judan Arazibagh ami? N…® kamagh…®n amuava, manmaghsua Judan Arazibar g…®n mangasa Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibav g…®a, me ab…®ri?‚Äù
\ms1 Gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itiba, merara // God…®n damazim…®n dera
\mr (Sapta 2:15--4:31)
\s1 Judaba ko Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba uaghara, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n ik…®t…®, // God suam, ia nan damazim…®n dera
\p 
\v 15 Egha Pol m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n Pita m…®gei, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra, e Judan gumazamizibara, egha ghaze, e ti bar dera. Ez…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibara, arazir kurabagh ami.
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt Onger Akaba 143:2; Aposel 13:38-39; 15:10-11; Rom 1:17; 3:20-28; 4:5; 11:6; Galesia 3:11; Hibru 7:18-19\x*Ez…® e fo, gumazamiziba Moses Osizirir Arazibar g…®n zuima, God kamagh…®n me m…®geir puvat…®, ia nan damazim…®n dera. Bar puvat…®. Gumazamiziba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n ik…®t…®, merara God kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ia nan damazim…®n dera. Kamagh…®n amiz…® e Krais Iesus n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an iti. E fo, gumazamiziba Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n mang…®t…®, God kamagh…®n me m…®kemeghan kogh suam, ia nan damazim…®n dera. N…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itir tuavimra God suam, ia nan damazim…®n dera. Ez…® Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n zuir tuavim puvat…®. God kamagh…®n e m…®k…®m suam, ia nan damazim…®n dera, kamaghsua, e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n iti.
\p 
\v 17-20 \x - \xo 2:17-20 \xt Jon 13:1; Rom 6:11; 6:14; 7:6; 2 Korin 5:15; Galesia 1:4; Efesus 5:2; 1 Tesalonika 5:10; Taitus 2:14; Hibru 9:14; 1 Pita 4:2; 1 Jon 3:8-9\x*‚ÄúE n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n ik…®t…®, God tuavir kam…®n suam, e an damazim…®n dera. Tuavir kam…®n e fo, e Judaba uaghan Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibar m…®n arazir kurabagh ami. Egh e ti kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, Krais uab…® arazir kurabar amuasa, gumazamiziba ab…®ri. Bar puvat…®. E, Moses Osirizir Araziba ategh…®va, kamagh…®n e arazir kurabagh amir puvat…®. K…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n Otarim…®n iti. A bar na gifuegha nan akurvaghasa uan m…®karzim gas…®ghas…®ki. Ez…® ik…®r…®m…®rir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n nguazir kam…®n amim, k…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n tuavim…®n g…®n ghuava, ik…®r…®m…®rir kam gami. K…® Krais ko ter ighuvim…®n aremegha, ik…®r…®m…®rir igiam ini. Ez…® ik…®r…®m…®rir kam a nan ik…®r…®m…®rimra puvat…®. Krais angam…®ra nan aven iti. K…® ik…®va God…®n ingangarim damuasa, kamagh…®n Moses Osirizir Araziba na gamiz…® k…® aremegha ua Moses Osirizir Arazibar gavgavim…®n apengan itir puvat…®. Bizir k…® Moses…®n Osirizir Arazibar apengan ikiava amiziba, k…® da ag…®fa. Egh g…®n ua dar amuva, kamagh…®n mati k…® arazir kurabagh amir gumazim.\f + \fr 2:17-20 \ft Grigh…®n akam, vez…®n kam…®n deragha bigha m…®kemezir puvat…®. Pol ti kamagh…®n m…®k…®masa, gumazamiziba Krais…®n g…®n mang…®, egh ua Moses Osirizir Arazibar apengan ikian kogham. Krais…®n g…®n zuir marazi, Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n mang…®s…® gavgavigh, egh me uaghan arazir kurabagh amibar otivigham, mati gumazamizir bar Moses Osirizir Arazibar apengan itibar m…®n iti. N…® Rom 7:4-6…®n gan.\f*
