\v 6-9 \x - \xo 3:6-9 \xt Jenesis 12:3; 15:6; 18:18; 22:18; Jon 8:39; Aposel 3:25; Rom 4:3; 4:11-16; 9:17; Jems 2:23\x*Ia Abraham…®n eghaghanim g…®n…®ghn…®gh. God fom…®ra kamagh…®n fo, g…®n Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Akar Aghuim…®n ik…®t…®, a kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m suam, ia nan damazim…®n dera. Ez…® God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®keme, God fom…®ra Akar Aghuim Abraham ganigha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® bang…®n, k…® nguazir kam…®n itir kantriba bar derav…®ra me damuam.‚Äù God…®n Ak…®nafarim ghaze, ‚ÄúAbraham n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n itima, ez…® God kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® nan damazim…®n dera.‚Äù Kamagh…®n, ia fogh suam, gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais Iesus…®n itiba, me uaghan Abraham…®n ovavir boriba. Abraham n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim itima, God derav…®ra a gami. Kamagh…®ra gumazamiziba bar n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ik…®t…®, a uaghan derav…®ra me damuam.
