\v 10-12 \x - \xo 3:10-12 \xt Ofa Gami 18:5; God…®n Araziba 27:26; Nehemia 9:29; Jeremaia 11:3; Habakuk 2:4; Rom 1:17; 10:5; 11:6; Galesia 2:16; Hibru 10:38\x*Moses Osirizir Arazibar m…®ngarim, a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n bizim puvat…®, a bizir igharazim. Ez…® God…®n Ak…®nafarim ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazamiziba Moses Osirizir Araziba m…®gei mogh…®n damu egh dughiaba zurara dar amut…®, arazir kaba me damut…®, me ik…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äù\f + \fr 3:10-12 \ft Gumazitam Moses Osirizir Araziba zurara bar derav…®ra tam…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®.\f* Egha God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam o amizitam n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ik…®t…®, God suam, n…® nan damazim…®n dera, gumazir kamra zurara derav…®ra ik…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äù Kamagh…®n, e bar fo, gumazitam o amizitam Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n ghua, God…®n damazim…®n derazir puvat…®. God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam o amizitam ak…®nafarim…®n aven itir araziba derav…®ra dar g…®n mangan koght…®, God gumazir kam gas…®ghasigham.‚Äù Eght…® kamagh…®n tina suam, e Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n mang…®va God…®n damazim…®n deragham, kamagh…®n amir gumazamiziba, God me gas…®ghas…®gham.
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt God…®n Araziba 21:23; Rom 8:3; 2 Korin 5:21; Galesia 4:5\x*Moses Osirizir Araziba kamagh…®n m…®keme, e gumazamiziba bar Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n mang…®va, egh ikuvigham. God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®keme, ‚ÄúGumazir ter ighuvim…®n duiba God ghaze, me gumazir kuraba.‚Äù Ez…® kamagh…®n Krais en akurvaghasa ziar kam ini, ‚Äúgumazir kuram.‚Äù Egha ziar kam bang…®n a uam e ini.
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Joel 2:28-29; Sekaraia 12:10; Aposel 2:33\x*God Abraham derav…®ra a gamigha ghaze, k…® Abraham gamiz…® mogh…®ra, k…® Krais Iesus…®n ingangarim…®n tuavim…®n Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba derav…®ra me damuam. Egha God kamagh…®n ifonge, e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais Iesus…®n ik…®va, an Duam iniam. Egha kamagh…®n a uam e ini.
