\v 19 \x - \xo 3:19 \xt God…®n Araziba 5:5; 5:22-27; Jon 1:17; Aposel 7:38; 7:53; Rom 5:20; Hibru 2:2\x*Ez…® kamagh…®n manmaghsua God uan osirizir araziba Moses gan…®ngi? God gumazamizibar amut…®, me arazir kurabar m…®ngarim g…®foghasa, uan osirizir araziba an…®ngi. God faragha akar d…®k…®r…®zim Abraham ganigha ghaze, n…®n ovavim gumazamiziba bar men akurvagham. Ez…® gumazir kam zuam…®ra izezir puvat…®. Ez…® arazir kurar kaba bagha, God g…®n uan osirizir araziba an…®ngi. A kamagh…®n ifonge, an osirizir araziba ik…® mang…®, ovavim otoghamin dughiam…®n tugham. God uan osirizir arazir kaba isa enselbar dafarim gat…®z…®, me da isa abuir gumazim Moses gan…®ngiz…®, abuir gumazim e gan…®ngi.
\v 20 \x - \xo 3:20 \xt Rom 3:29-30\x*Egh gumazitam ingangaritam damus…® gumazir igharazitam ko Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim ak…®rs…®, an a is…®va abuir gumazim…®n dafarim dat…®ght…®ma, abuir gumazim a is…®va gumazir igharazim dan…®ngan kogham. Ez…® God uab…®ra, a uab…® uan Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim Abraham gan…®ngi, egha ensel…®n tam gan…®ngizir puvat…®, o abuir gumazitam gan…®ngizir puvat…®.
