\v 23 Faraghav…®ra n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir kam izezir puvat…®z…®, arazir kurabar gavgavim e ikiaghar…®ghiz…®, e Moses Osirizir Arazibar apengan iti. Egh mang…® God n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n tuavim en akaghamin dughiam otogham.
