\v 9-10 \x - \xo 4:9-10 \xt Rom 8:3; 14:15; 1 Korin 8:3; Kolosi 2:16-20; Hibru 7:18\x*Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia God…®n borogh…®n zui. O k…® kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, God ian borogh…®n zui. Ia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, ia zurara Moses Osirizir Arazibar dughiar ekiaba ko iak…®nir igiabar dughiaba ko azenir igiabar dughiaba ko dagheba otir dughiabar g…®n mangam. Manmaghsua ia ua nguazim ko overiam…®n bizibagh ativagha dar garir pura duar kurabar g…®n zui? Da gavgaviba puvat…®. Ia ti uamategh dar ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar ikiasa?
