\s1 Ia nan arazibar g…®n iz…®
\p 
\v 12-15 \x - \xo 4:12-15 \xt 1 Korin 2:3; 2 Korin 11:30; 12:7-9\x*Nan adarasi, k…® uab…® Moses Osirizir Araziba ategha ian m…®n iti. Ez…® ia nan m…®n ikiasa k…® ia gakaghori. Ia fo, fom…®ra k…® Galesian Provins…®n izeghava, nguibar igharazitam…®n mangasava amuava ar…®mariam ini. Egha dughiar kamra Akar Aghuim faragha ia m…®k…®ni. Nan m…®karzim gavgavim puvat…®gha os…®mt…®zir ekiam ia gan…®ngi. Ez…® ia ak…®rim ragha na gasarazir puvat…®, egha na ko ikian aghuazir puvat…®. Ensel…®n tam, o Krais Iesus uab…® iz…®va ia ko ik…®t…®, ia aning inigh bar derav…®ra aning damuam. Ez…® k…® areir dughiam…®n, ia na inighava arazir kamra na gami. Ia na iniz…® k…® ian gara itima, ia arazir kuratam na gamizir puvat…®. K…® guizbang…®ra kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, dughiar kam…®n ia nan akurvaghasa bar ifonge. Egha ia uan damaziba na bagha da asiasa ifuegha da asigha na ganighai. Ia faragha na gifuegha na bagha bar akonge. Ez…® ia na gifongezir navir kam dat…®r…®gh…®n managh iti?
\v 16 \x - \xo 4:16 \xt Amos 5:10; Galesia 2:14\x*Manmagh…®n ami? K…® guizbang…®ra akam ia m…®k…®ni, egha kamagh…®n k…® ti ian apanim gava?
\p 
\v 17 Ifavarir gumazir kaba kamagh…®n ifonge, ia me baghav…®ra ikiasa, me pura ian kuariba isava, egha guizbang…®ra ian akurvaghamin n…®ghn…®ziba puvat…®. Ia men n…®ghn…®zibar g…®n mang…®va egh ia en saghon ikiasa, me ifonge.
\v 18 Tina gumazamizir igharaziba baghv…®ra ik…®, egh men akurvaghamin n…®ghn…®zir aghuim ik…®t…®, kamagh…®n dera. Ia zurara arazir kam damuv…®ra ik…®. Egh k…® ia ko ikiamin dughiabara puvat…®.\f + \fr 4:18 \ft Grigh…®n akam vez…®n kam…®n deragha bigha m…®kemezir puvat…®.\f*
\v 19-20 K…® orazi, ia arazir kam gamima, k…® ia bagha okam n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, k…® manmagh…®n ian akurvagham. K…® ia ko itir puvat…®, Iavzika. K…® ia ko ikia, ti tong akar aghuitam ia m…®kemeghai. Nan boriba, ia guizbang…®ra God…®n boribagh avagh…®va Krais…®n m…®n ikiasa, kamagh…®n k…® ia bagha ua m…®zazir kam barasi. Mati amizim borim batasa isir m…®zazim.
\s1 Hagar ko Sara
\p 
\v 21-23 \x - \xo 4:21-23 \xt Jenesis 16:15; 21:2\x*\x - \xo 4:21-23 \xt Jenesis 18:10-14; Rom 9:7-9; Hibru 11:11\x*Ia gumazamizir Moses Osirizir Arazibar apengan ikiasa ifongeziba ia na m…®k…®m. Ia ti Moses Osirizir Araziba m…®kemez…® mogh…®n fozir puvat…®? God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®keme, Abraham otarir pumuning iti. Ingangarir amizir k…®nim, Hagar, mam bate. Ez…® guizbang…®ra an amuim, Sara, mam bate. Ingangarir amizir k…®nim…®n borim nguazim…®n amiziba boriba isi mogh…®n oto. Ez…® guizbang…®ra an amuim…®n borim, an akar d…®k…®r…®zim…®n tuavim…®n oto.
\v 24-25 \x - \xo 4:24-25 \xt Rom 8:15; Galesia 5:1\x*Amizir kamning Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir pumuning…®n m…®n iti. Eghaghanir kamnagh akar is…®n zuim an iti. Hagar, a Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n m…®n iti. Sainain M…®ghs…®am, a kantri Arebian iti. Hagar ingangarir amizir k…®nir mam. Ez…® an boriba uaghan ingangarir gumazir k…®niba. Hagar uan boriba ko me ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar m…®n ti. Ez…® Jerusalem…®n dat…®r…®gh…®n itim, an Hagar…®n m…®n iti. Dat…®r…®gh…®n itir Jerusalem uan boriba ko, me Moses Osirizir Arazibar apengan ikia ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar m…®n ami.
\v 26-27 \x - \xo 4:26-27 \xt Aisaia 54:1; Hibru 12:22; Akar Mogomem 3:12; 21:2; 21:10\x*God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®keme:
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúAmizir boriba puvat…®zir kam, n…®n boriba g…®n bar av…®rasemegham.
\q2 N…® mati amizir n…®n pam n…® ataghizim.
\q1 Egh n…® g…®n borir bar av…®riba inight…®,
\q2 n…®n boribar d…®bobonim,
\q3 amizir uan pam ko itim…®n boribar, d…®bobonim gafiragham.
\q1 Kamagh…®n n…® amizir boriba isir puvat…®zim, n…® bar akongegh.
\q2 N…® amizir ot…®r…®m…®rir m…®zazibagh fozir puvat…®zim,
\q3 n…®n navim deragh, n…® bar akuegh,
\q4 pamtem d…®m…®va araghas…®.‚Äù
\b
\m Ez…® kamagh…®n Jerusalem…®n igharazim a God…®n Nguibam…®n iti, Moses Osirizir Araziba a ikiaghar…®gh…®zir puvat…®z…®ma, a dat…®r…®gh…®n f…®riagh…®r…®. Ez…® an en amebam…®n m…®n iti.\f + \fr 4:26-27 \ft Ves 22…®n aven, Pol Sara d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra Abraham…®n amuim, Sara.‚Äù Kar akar is…®n zuir mam, Sara God…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zim…®n m…®n iti. Saran otarim Aisak, a Krais…®n g…®n zuir darazir m…®n iti. N…® Galesia 4:28…®n gan.\f*
\v 28 \x - \xo 4:28 \xt Aposel 3:25; Rom 9:7-8; Galesia 3:29\x*Ez…® nan adarasi, ia Aisak…®n m…®n ami. God…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zim m…®rara, ia an boriba.
\v 29 \x - \xo 4:29 \xt Jenesis 21:9; Galesia 5:11; 6:12\x*Nguazim…®n amiziba boriba isi mogh…®n otozir otarim, a God…®n Duam…®n gavgavim…®n otozir otarim pazava a gami. Kamagh…®ra, dat…®r…®gh…®n Moses Osirizir Arazibar apengan itir gumazamiziba, e tina God…®n Duam…®n apengan iti, me en aghuagha os…®mt…®ziba e gar…®si.
\v 30 \x - \xo 4:30 \xt Jenesis 21:10; Jon 8:35\x*Ez…® God…®n Ak…®nafarim manmagh…®n m…®keme? A kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIngangarir amizir k…®nim…®n borim, a guizbang…®ra Abraham…®n amuim…®n borim ko afeziam…®n bizir aghuiba da inian kogham. Kamagh…®n, n…® ingangarir amizir k…®nim uan otarim ko aning batokegh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 31 \x - \xo 4:31 \xt Jon 8:36; Galesia 3:29; 5:1; 5:13\x*Nan adarasi, e ingangarir amizir k…®nim…®n boriba puvat…®, e guizbang…®ra Abraham…®n amuim…®n boriba.
\c 5
\ms1 God…®n gumazamiziba f…®riagh…®re
\mr (Sapta 5--6)
\s1 Ia uari bagh ganigh, Moses Osirizir Araziba ua ia ik…®rarighan kogham
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 5:1 \xt Jon 8:32; 8:36; Aposel 15:10; Rom 6:18; Galesia 2:4; 5:13; 1 Pita 2:16\x*Krais, e Moses Osirizir Arazibar apengan ikian aghuaghava, kamagh…®n an e gamiz…®, e f…®riagh…®r…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia tuivigh gavgafigh. Ia gumazamizitabar gant…®, me ua ia damut…®, ia ua ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar m…®n ikian mark…®.
\p 
\v 2 Ia na baragh. K…® Pol, k…® ia m…®gei, ia men gant…®ma me ian m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghoreght…®ma, Krais…®n ingangarim tong bar ian akuraghan kogham. Bar puvat…®.
\v 3 \x - \xo 5:3 \xt Galesia 3:10\x*K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ua derav…®ra kamagh…®n ia m…®k…®masa, n…® tina gumazitam…®n gant…®, a n…®n m…®karzir mogomem…®n inim atught…®, kamagh…®n n…® uaghan Moses Osirizir Araziba bar dar g…®n mangam.
\v 4 \x - \xo 5:4 \xt Rom 9:31-32; Hibru 12:15\x*Ia gumazamizir Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n mangasava amiba, ez…® tuavir kam…®n ia ghaze, e God…®n damazim…®n dera, ia kamagh…®n Krais ategha g…®fa. Ia God…®n apangkuvim…®n tuavim ategha g…®fa.
\v 5-6 \x - \xo 5:5-6 \xt Rom 8:24-25; 1 Korin 7:19; Galesia 6:15; Kolosi 3:11; 2 Timoti 4:8; Jems 2:18-22\x*Egh gumazim Krais Iesus ko ik…®t…®, gumazibar m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghorir arazim, a pura bizim, egh gumazibar m…®karzir mogomebar inibar aghorir puvat…®zir arazim, a uaghan pura bizim. Ez…®ma gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim itim, an n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim a gamima, a bar gumazir igharazibagh ifonge, kar guizbang…®n bizim. God…®n Duam…®n gavgavim…®n, e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n iti. Egha e, dughiar God suam, ia nan damazim…®n derazim, m…®zuai.
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 5:7 \xt 1 Korin 9:24; Galesia 1:6; 3:1\x*Ia fom…®ra deraghav…®ra Krais…®n tuavim…®n zui. Ez…® tina tuavim ap…®riz…®ma ia ua guizbang…®n akam…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®?
\v 8 N…®ghn…®zir ia dat…®r…®gh…®n g…®nt…®zim, a God…®n ian diazim…®n izezir puvat…®.
\v 9 \x - \xo 5:9 \xt 1 Korin 5:6; 15:33\x*Yis…®n muziarim, a bret bar a damight…®, a buigham.
\v 10 \x - \xo 5:10 \xt 2 Korin 2:3; 10:6; 11:15; Galesia 1:7\x*K…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti, Ekiam ian akuragham. Egh ia nan n…®ghn…®zim…®n g…®n mang…®va, n…®ghn…®zir igharazim atakigh. K…® fozir pu, tina ian n…®ghn…®zibagh as…®ghas…®si. Gumazamizir kaba arazir kurar ia gamizim bagh ivezir kuram iniam.
\v 11 \x - \xo 5:11 \xt 1 Korin 1:23; 15:30; Galesia 6:12; 6:17\x*Nan adarasi, ia orakigh, gumazir maba ghaze, Pol gumaziba uan m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghorir akam dughiabar anekurav…®ra iti. Egh me guizbang…®ra kamagh…®n n…®ghnigh, me tizim bagha os…®mt…®zim na gar…®si? Kar guizbang…®ra n…®ghn…®zim puvat…®. Ez…® k…® ter ighuvim…®n akam akurima, akar kam gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®zibagh as…®ghas…®si. Egh k…® m…®karzir mogomem…®n inim aghorir akam akun…®va, ter ighuvim…®n akam akunan koght…®, ter ighuvim…®n akar gumazibar n…®ghn…®zibagh as…®gh…®s…®zim, a pura akar am…®rizim…®n m…®n otogh, ua gumazibar n…®ghn…®zibagh as…®ghas…®ghan kogham.
\v 12 Gumazir ian navibagh inivir kaba, me m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghoramin arazim bagha bar gavgafi. Kamagh…®n me uarira uan inibar ghor, magh suegh bar dar ghoregh.
\p 
\v 13-15 \x - \xo 5:13-15 \xt Ofa Gami 19:18; Matyu 5:43; 7:12; Rom 13:8-9; 1 Korin 8:9; 9:19; 1 Pita 2:16; 2 Pita 2:16-19; Jems 2:8\x*Nan adarasi, ia f…®righ…®rasa God ifonge, egha kamagh…®n a ian dia. Eght…® ia ua Moses Osirizir Arazibar apengan ikian kogh kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…® suam, ‚ÄúMoses Osirizir Araziba e ikiaghar…®ghiz…®, e arazir kaba ategha f…®riagh…®re. Egh e navir ghurim…®n arazibar amuam.‚Äù Moses Osirizir Arazibar m…®g…®r…®g…®aba, da bar uari inigha akar vam…®ran iti, ‚ÄúN…® uab…®ra uab…® gifongez…® mogh…®n, gumazamizir igharazibagh ifongegh.‚Äù Ia bar God…®n gumazamizibar ingangarir gumazamizibar m…®n ik…®, uarira uarigh ifongegh. Egh ia uarir atar pura tintinibar uariv sogh, egh derav…®ra n…®ghn…®gh. Ia uarigh as…®ghas…®gham.
\s1 God…®n Duam n…®n sure gamir arazir aghuibar g…®n mang…®
\p 
\v 16-18 \x - \xo 5:16-18 \xt Rom 6:12-14; 7:15-23; 8:2-7; 8:14; 13:14; Galesia 5:25; 1 Pita 2:11\x*God…®n Duam koma n…®n navir ghurim, bizir kamning uaning…®n apanimning gami. God…®n Duam ghaze, n…® God…®n arazir aghuibara damu. Ez…® kamagh…®n n…® dar amuasa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, n…® arazir aghuibar g…®n mang…®s…® damut…®, n…®n navir ghurim…®n araziba suam, mark…®. N…®n navir ghurim suam, ‚ÄúArazir kuratam damu.‚Äù Eght…® n…® tam damuam. Kamagh…®n n…® arazir kurabar g…®n mang…®t…®, God…®n Duam suam, markiam. E fo, navir ghurim…®n araziba God…®n Duam d…®kab…®nasa. Ez…® God…®n Duam navir ghurim…®n araziba d…®kab…®nasa. Aning uaning adosi. Ez…® bizir ia damuasa ifongezim, ia a damighan kogham. Ia God…®n Duam…®n g…®n mang…®va, Moses Osirizir Arazibar apengan ikian kogham. Egh, ia navir ghurim…®n arazibar g…®n mangan kogham. Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, ia navir ghurim…®n araziba ateght…®ma, God…®n Duamra ian faraght…®ma, ia an g…®n mang…®.
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 5:19 \xt 1 Korin 3:3; 6:9-10; Efesus 5:3; Kolosi 3:5; Jems 3:14-15\x*Ia navir ghurim…®n arazibagh fogha g…®fa. Arazir kaba, gumazamiziba tintinibar uari koma akua arazir m…®z…®r…®zibagh amuava, afiar arazibagh ami.
\v 20 Egha nguazir kam…®n biziba e God gami mogh…®n e uari isa dagh an…®di, imezibagh amir arazibagh amuava, munav…®n biziba bagha navim ikuvigha da iniasa navim isi. Egha atara bizibagh as…®ghas…®si, uarir apanibagh ami, gumazamizir igharazibar aghuagha, uab…®ra uab…® g…®n…®ghn…®si, biziba bagha uari batogha uari ab…®si.
\v 21 \x - \xo 5:21 \xt 1 Korin 6:9; Efesus 5:5; Kolosi 3:6; Akar Mogomem 22:15\x*Egha d…®par onganiba apava onganigha, pura gumazamiziba isa pamtem…®n diava ighiar kurabar arazibagh ami. Egha arazir kurar maba uaghan kamagh…®n iti. K…® fom…®ra ia m…®kemegha g…®fa. Egha k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n akar kamra ua ia m…®gei. Gumazamizir arazir kabagh amiba, me God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven mangan kogham.
\p 
\v 22-23 \x - \xo 5:22-23 \xt 1 Korin 13:7; Efesus 5:9; Kolosi 3:12; 1 Timoti 1:9; Jems 3:17\x*Ez…® God…®n Duam arazir aghuir kabar amuasava en naviba fe: arazir bar igharaz darazigh ifongezim, bar akongezim, navir am…®rizim, dughorir am…®razim, gumazibar akurvagha arazir aghuibar me gami. Egha guizbang…®ra m…®g…®a derav…®ra bizibagh amua, gumazibar asughasusi, egha navir ghurim…®n araziba d…®kab…®ri. Moses Osirizir Arazitam arazir kabar anogoroghezir puvat…®.
\v 24 \x - \xo 5:24 \xt Rom 6:6; Kolosi 3:5; 1 Pita 2:11\x*Gumazamizir Krais Iesus…®n g…®n zuiba, me navir ghurim…®n araziba ko biziba bagha bar ifongezir arazir kuraba inigha, ter ighuvim…®n da gura. Egha dagh afuz…®ma, da aremegha g…®fa.
\v 25 \x - \xo 5:25 \xt Rom 8:4-5; Galesia 5:16\x*God…®n Duam ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim e gan…®ngi. Kamagh…®n, anar…®ra e ko daruva en akurvagham.
\v 26 \x - \xo 5:26 \xt Filipai 2:3\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e pura uarira uan ziaba fan kogham. Egh e igharaz darazir navibagh inivt…®, me uarir ataran kogham. Egh e men biziba bagh naviba isian kogham.
\c 6
\s1 Bizir manam n…® uan navir averiam…®n an opari, bizir kamnagh…®ra, an otogham
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 6:1 \xt Matyu 18:15; 1 Korin 2:15; 4:21; 2 Timoti 2:25; Hibru 12:13; Jems 5:19\x*Nan adarasi, ian tav arazir kuratam damight…®, ia gumazir God…®n Duam…®n g…®n zuiba, ia navir am…®rizim…®n arazibar a damuva, an akuraght…®, a uan arazir kuraba ategham. Kamagh…®n ia derav…®ra uari bagh gan, Satan ia gifaraght…®ma, ia uaghan arazir kuratam damigham.
\v 2-3 \x - \xo 6:2-3 \xt Jon 13:14-15; Rom 12:3; 15:1; 1 Korin 8:2; 2 Korin 3:5; 1 Tesalonika 5:14; 1 Jon 4:21\x*Eght…® gumazitam suam, a ziar ekiam iti, puvat…®, a ziam pu, egha kamagh…®n gumazir kam uab…®ra uab…® gifari. Ia igharaz darazir akuragh men os…®mt…®ziba ater. Egh ia kamagh…®n damuva, guizbang…®ra Krais…®n arazibar g…®n mangam.
\v 4-5 \x - \xo 6:4-5 \xt Rom 2:6; 14:12; 1 Korin 3:8; 11:28; 2 Korin 13:5\x*Gumazamiziba bar, me uari uan arazir me amibar os…®mt…®ziba ateram. Gumazamiziba uari uan ingangaribar gan, da deras ti puvat…®. Gumazamiziba kamagh…®n damuva, me uari uan arazibar gan dagh ifongegh. Egh me uan arazibar gan, egh gumazir igharazim…®n arazibara gan dav k…®man mark…®.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 6:6 \xt Rom 15:27; 1 Korin 9:11; 9:14\x*Gumazir God…®n akam barazim, a uan bizir aghuitaba an sure gamir gumazim dan…®ng.
\p 
\v 7-8 \x - \xo 6:7-8 \xt Jop 13:9; Hosea 8:7; Luk 16:25; Jon 3:6; 6:63; Rom 2:6; 8:13; 1 Korin 6:9; 10:12; Jems 3:18\x*Bizir manam n…® uan navir averiam…®n anekara, bizir kamnagh…®ra, an otogham. Gumazitam o amizitam uan navir ghurim…®n arazibar g…®n mang…®t…®ma, an navir ghurir kam…®n dagher kuraba otivt…®ma a bar ikuvigham. Egh gumazitam o amizitam God…®n Duam…®n g…®n mang…®t…®, God…®n Duam a damut…®, dagher aghuiba otivt…®ma, a ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuir zurara itim iniam. Egh ia suam, ia God gifari, bar puvat…®. Ia uarira uarigh ifar…®va, kamagh…®n damuan mark…®.
\v 9 \x - \xo 6:9 \xt 1 Korin 15:58; 2 Tesalonika 3:13; Hibru 3:6; 3:14; Akar Mogomem 2:10\x*Egh e ingangarim damus…® am…®rvaghan kogh, dagheba iniamin dughiam…®n, e dagher bar aghuiba iniam. Kamagh…®n e arazir aghuibar amus…® am…®rvaghan kogham.
\v 10 \x - \xo 6:10 \xt 1 Tesalonika 5:15; 1 Timoti 6:18\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, dat…®r…®gh…®n dughiam ikiav…®ra iti, e arazir aghuibar gumazamizir igharaziba bar derav…®ra me damuam. Egh bizir ekiam, e derav…®ra gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Ekiam…®n itibar amuam.
\s1 Pol…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar abuananaba
\p 
\v 11 K…® osirizir osizirir ekiar kaba, ia dar gari, kar k…® uab…® uan dafarim…®n osirizir akaba.\f + \fr 6:11 \ft N…® akar 1 Korin 16:21…®n itim…®n gan.\f*
\p 
\v 12-13 \x - \xo 6:12-13 \xt Galesia 2:3; 2:14; 5:11; Filipai 3:18\x*Ifavarir gumaziba atiatia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, ‚ÄúGumazir igharaziba kamagh…®n fogh suam, e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n ter ighuvim…®n iti, egh me paz…® e damuam.‚Äù Kamagh…®n me ian m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghorasa bar gavgafi. Me ghaze, me ian m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghoreght…®, gumaziba bizir kam bagh men ziaba fam. Ez…® gumazir uan m…®karzibar iniba aghorezir kabanagh, uaghan derav…®ra Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®. Ia oragh. Gumazir kaba ian m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghorasa bar gavgafi. Me kamaghsua, me kamagh…®n ia damigh gumazir igharazibar damazim…®n ziar ekiaba iniasa.
\v 14-15 \x - \xo 6:14-15 \xt Rom 2:29; 6:6; 1 Korin 1:31; 2:2; 2 Korin 5:17; Galesia 5:6; Filipai 3:3; Kolosi 3:11\x*Ez…® m…®karzir mogomem…®n inim aghorir arazim, a pura bizim. Egha m…®karzir mogomem…®n inim aghorir puvat…®zir arazim, a uaghan pura bizim. God e gamiz…®ma e gumazamizir igiabar otifi, kar bizir ekiam. En Ekiam Krais Iesus ter ighuvim…®n areme. Ez…® k…® bizir kam bagha uan ziam o gumazir igharazitam…®n ziam fer puvat…®. K…® God…®n ziamra fe. Iesus ter ighuvim…®n areme, ez…® tuavir kam…®n nguazir kam…®n araziba nan n…®ghn…®zim…®n aremegha g…®fa. Egha mati k…® uab…® ter ighuvim…®n areme. Egh k…® uam nguazir kam…®n arazibar g…®n mangan kogham.
\v 16 N…®ghn…®zir kam…®n suiragha an g…®nt…®ziba, God…®n apangkuvim men ikiam. Egh a men navibar amut…®ma me n…®m…®ra ikiam. Eght…® gumazamizir kaba, me guizbang…®ra God…®n Israelia.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 6:17 \xt 2 Korin 1:5; 4:10; 11:23; Galesia 5:11; Kolosi 1:24\x*Gumaziba na m…®soghez…®, men duar kuriba nan m…®karzim…®n iti. Ia bizir kabar gan suam, k…® guizbang…®n Iesus…®n ingangarir gumazim. Eght…® gumazitam uam os…®mt…®zitam na dar…®ghan k…® aghua.
